== 工程建设 ==
2006年6月25日，塞萨洛尼基地铁正式动工，由於挖掘時多次發現古蹟和經歷了[[希臘國債危機|國債危機]]，工程數度延期，大部分路段將會於2023年開通。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Robert Schwandl |title=THESSALONIKI Metro |url=http://www.urbanrail.net/eu/gr/thessaloniki/thessal.htm |website=urbanrail.net |accessdate=2020-02-04 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116220624/http://www.urbanrail.net/eu/gr/thessaloniki/thessal.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Giorgos Christides |title=Thessaloniki metro: Ancient dilemma for modern Greece |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-21743758 |accessdate=2020-02-04 |work=BBC |date=14 Mar 2013 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116220627/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-21743758 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

